# Codex Memory Index

Compact index injected into `~/.codex/AGENTS.md` by `~/rebuild-codex-agents-md.sh`.
Treat these entries as stable context. Read the detail file only when relevant.

## High Priority Facts

- Owner identity: who you are, your Discord user_id, primary group.
- Bot peers: which other AI bots share your Discord group.
- Output style preferences: language, emoji prefix, formatting.
- Security model active in this deployment.

