## Write Policy

- Save only when the owner explicitly asks OR a task produces durable operating facts future sessions need.
- Keep `MEMORY.md` compact. Details go in typed memory files, linked here.
- No secrets / tokens / cookies / private keys / one-time codes.
- After edit: run `~/rebuild-codex-agents-md.sh`, then start a new Codex session when immediate load is needed.
